doctype html
html
  head
    title Trinh Nguyen's blog | vespaiach.com
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    each item in links
      link(rel="stylesheet", href=item)
    each item in scripts
      script(src=item)

  body
    header(id="top")
      div(class='header')
        div(class='bio')
          img(src='/images/vespaiach.jpeg', title='Trinh Nguyen', alt='Trinh Nguyen', class='bio-avatar')
          div(class='bio-text')
            h2 Trinh Nguyen
            p.
              Hey lovely people of the internet! I'm a computer enthusiast and software engineer with a deep love for all things web tech and open source. 
              You'll often find me lost in the world of coding, crafting digital wonders from scratch.
              Join me as I navigate the wild terrain of tech trends, sharing my discoveries and geeky musings along the way. 
              So, whether you're a seasoned developer or just curious about the digital realm, let's embark on a tech-filled adventure together. 
              Here's to endless lines of code and the joy of creating something awesome!
        div(class='tags')
          a(href='#', data-tag='all') All::#{total}
          each tag, index in tags
            a(href='#', data-tag=tag.slug) #{tag.slug}::#{tag.count}

    div(class="content", id="content")
      each item in frontmatters
        section(class="excerpt", data-tags=item.tags)

          div(class="post-meta")
